subject: Automobile Racing
Nascar Sprint Cup Series
lead_paragraph: Matt Kenseth pushed Kevin Harvick down the stretch and took the lead for good when Harvick, the defending series champion, ran out of gas Sunday at the Sylvania 300, the second race of the Chase for the Nascar Sprint Cup.
